name: Cake Health
description: CakeHealth brings all your health care plans together online so you can easily track your health spending — without the paperwork.

name: CORAlink
description: An emergency app that stores emergency lifesaving information such as profile, blood type, allergies and medications with a notification feature for emergency contact showing the GPS coordinates of the location of emergency.

name: CORAvault
description: CORAVault™ allows users to carry an always up-to-date health record, manage appointments, share their records in a secure manner and even manage their medications and allergies through the application.

name: Datuit
description: With Datuit’s Care Plan Manager, you can communicate with all of your clinicians and caregivers at the same time.  Information is accurately and conveniently communicated, providing information to your entire care team, and your providers can share your clinical health information with you and with each other.

name: FollowMyHealth
description: Empowers patients to take a more active role in managing their care.

name: Gazelle
description: Get your lab results on your smartphone with Gazelle.\nLife is complicated. Managing your health shouldn’t be.

name: GenieMD
description: GenieMD easily tracks, securely stores and conveniently shares your health profile from the palm of your hand.

name: Healthvault
description: A trusted place for people to gather, store, use, and share health information online.

name: Hello Doctor
description: Hello Doctor helps you manage and understand your medical records, and makes it easy to share them with your doctor, for free. No more binders full of papers!\n\n

name: iBlueButton
description: Easily access and share their health records with their physicians, anywhere and anytime.

name: Ice Blue Button
description: ICEBlueButton allows anyone to easily create an ICE (In Case of Emergency) record on their smartphone for themselves and their loved ones.

name: MedYear
description: Personal health exchange. Download your records securely into an account you control. Easily share your information however you want.

name: MyFamily
description: Lyfechannel helps patients build the dietary, physical activity and prescription drug adherence habits to meet their chronic disease demands\n\n

name: NoMoreClipboard
description: Securely organize, update, access and share medical information online. Free NoMoreClipboard Personal Health Records are Better. Managed.\n\n

name: Prime
description: Prime lets you automatically get your health records from any doctor and allows you to easily access and use your personal health info anywhere you go.\n\n

name: Swellbox
description: Swellbox brings your health information together.
